snippet.title: Graham Wardle & Amber Marshall | Heartland season 12
snippet.description:
Actors and Heartland stars Graham Wardle & Amber Marshall sat down with us at CBC in Toronto to talk about the 12th season of the series, how their roles have evolved, and working with babies and animals.
